{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=4a1b80c9ff193dd0d367438ccc0874e0&src=http%3A%2F%2Ff.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F5243fbf2b21193130d406a9c6d380cd791238d9f.jpg","summary":"赤峰学院是2003年4月16日经国家教育部批准，由赤峰民族师范高等专科学校、赤峰教育学院、内蒙古广播电视大学赤峰分校三所专科层次的高校合并，同时并入赤峰卫校、内蒙古幼儿师范学校的部分资源组建的一所多学科、综合性普通本科高等学校。学院诞生在世界闻名的“红山文化”发祥地—赤峰市。截至2018年5月，学校占地面积780亩，规划占地面积1800亩，建筑面积23.38万平方米，固定资产总值6.8亿元。图书馆馆藏纸质图书120.8万册，电子图书61.6万种，中外文数据库33个。共25个教学机构，开设51个本科专业。有专任教师1038人，全日制在校生12883人。","tags":["综合类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"2003","所在地区":"赤峰市西郊","院校隶属":"内蒙古自治区教育厅","硕士点":"2"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493477&di=9f73ea4eb132dfb10373e5073730cf18&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3731558788%2C748447721%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493477&di=ff54c895f046fd1a888050de81f5ebcc&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3455010855%2C4000402557%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493477&di=51c8b065f91458cdda930b3edecd32dc&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3701731281%2C1004253977%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493477&di=ee70200e2747e05b952720815dfed761&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3705078413%2C927662858%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493477&di=a34494d326ce55df6ab4ae8d3ba3a9cc&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3714511455%2C822665076%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&